input.command:
curl -s -X POST http://rec-agent-api:8000/v1/messages \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "domain": "movie",
    "message": "Good day. I am seeking recommendations for motion pictures that I might find intellectually rewarding. I have a particular interest in comparative literature — I study how narratives travel across cultures and literary traditions — and I find that the finest films share something of that same quality: a story that resonates beyond the boundaries of the culture that produced it. I am not looking for anything violent or disturbing. Something that rewards careful attention would be most welcome. Where shall we begin?"
  }'

